Why Does mid / cols and mid % cols Work?

For a matrix with 4 columns:

Virtual Index	Row (index / cols)	Col (index % cols)	Value
0	0	0	1
1	0	1	3
2	0	2	5
3	0	3	7
4	1	0	10
5	1	1	11
6	1	2	16
7	1	3	20
8	2	0	23

This mapping lets us perform Binary Search without flattening the matrix.

